A modern YouTube clone replicating YouTube's 2025 interface, featuring a responsive video grid, search functionality, and a unique 
speed monitoring system. The app displays live speeds (0â€“120 km/h),when the person is driving, shows an eye-catching warning when speed exceeds 80 km/h along with a warning sound 
